Comment: This is a TERRIBLE defense against the Patzer, as QxPe5+ gives white Rh8.
That isn't much of a defense.
White must watch out for QxBe2#.  We don't want this game to end too quickly.  Pd3 will protect the bishop at Pe2, while letting white's black bishop access to the field.
